<normalizedToken id="1D5834E7C37B452D2A15F9C4B8C7D7FA" originalValue="XI–">XI-</normalizedToken>
15.XII.1890; 1 male, 1 female, same as lectotype but 20.
<normalizedToken id="0393877CE08B80744EA41D8467805E46" originalValue="IX–">IX-</normalizedToken>
15.X.1890. Holotype male 
<taxonomicName id="FA146CAF5EA63980ABA1DDDF98C84180" genus="Acridina" lsidName="Acridina helonoma" pageId="45" pageNumber="82" rank="species" species="helonoma">helonoma</taxonomicName>
